Class Parameters

java.lang.Object
engine.launcher.Parameters
public class Parameters extends Object
The Parameters class represents the various settings and parameters required for the simulation.

  • Constructor Details

    • Parameters

      public Parameters(int WIDTH, int HEIGHT, org.joml.Vector4f CELL_COLOR_A, org.joml.Vector4f CELL_COLOR_B, float EVAPORATE_SPEED, float DIFFUSE_SPEED, int AGENTS_COUNT, float CELL_B_PROBABILITY, SpawnMode SPAWN_MODE, float SENSOR_ANGLE_SPACING_A, float TURN_SPEED_A, float SENSOR_OFFSET_DISTANCE_A, int SENSOR_SIZE_A, float SENSOR_ANGLE_SPACING_B, float TURN_SPEED_B, float SENSOR_OFFSET_DISTANCE_B, int SENSOR_SIZE_B)
      Constructor that initializes the parameters with the provided values.
      Parameters:
      WIDTH - The width of the simulation window.
      HEIGHT - The height of the simulation window.
      CELL_COLOR_A - The color of A cells.
      CELL_COLOR_B - The color of B cells.
      EVAPORATE_SPEED - The evaporation speed setting.
      DIFFUSE_SPEED - The diffusion speed setting.
      AGENTS_COUNT - The number of agents in the simulation.
      CELL_B_PROBABILITY - The probability of spawning a B cell.
      SPAWN_MODE - The spawn mode setting.
      SENSOR_ANGLE_SPACING_A - The sensor angle spacing for A cells.
      TURN_SPEED_A - The turn speed for A cells.
      SENSOR_OFFSET_DISTANCE_A - The sensor offset distance for A cells.
      SENSOR_SIZE_A - The sensor size for A cells.
      SENSOR_ANGLE_SPACING_B - The sensor angle spacing for B cells.
      TURN_SPEED_B - The turn speed for B cells.
      SENSOR_OFFSET_DISTANCE_B - The sensor offset distance for B cells.
      SENSOR_SIZE_B - The sensor size for B cells.
